long_description: This Chaco dog collar extends the benefit of rugged Chaco webbing from your sandals to your canine companion. Outfit your dog for adventure with this strong and durable collar. Collar features a sturdy quick-release buckle, a metal ring for tags and a plastic clip for a safety light (safety light not included). Closeout.
